collection.name: ASM AIFA All-Stars
collection.description:
40,000 football characters, fast, fun, fully 3D rigged, all-unique and All-Stars!

The Artificial Intelligence Football Association (AIFA), is a forthcoming decentralised play-to-earn soccer game brought to you by Altered State Machine (ASM), the world’s premier protocol for Non-Fungible Intelligence. 

Configure your team, pair them with ASM Brains, and train them to rise to the top of the AIFA Championships… or take your favourite animated All-Star for adventures in other metaverses!

Join the team at [AIFA](https://aifa.football)
